{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_vrtx_01UNi2rFpm63hoReQGWTxFV5","type":"tool_result","content":"1\tapiVersion: machineconfiguration.openshift.io/v1\n2\tkind: MachineConfig\n3\tmetadata:\n4\t  name: test-config\n5\tspec:\n6\t  osImageURL: registry.example.com/oscontainer@sha256:b5bb9d8014a0f9b1d61e21e796d78dccdf1352f23cd32812f4850b878ae4944c\n7\t  kernelArguments:\n8\t    - foo=bar\n9\t    - nosmt\n10\t  config:\n11\t    ignition:\n12\t      version: \"2.2.0\"\n13\t    storage:\n14\t      files:\n15\t        -\n16\t          contents:\n17\t            source: \"data:,GROUP%3Dstable%0ASERVER%3Dhttp%3A%2F%2Flocalhost%3A32003%2Fv1%2Fupdate%0A\"\n18\t            verification: {}\n19\t          filesystem: root\n20\t          mode: 420\n21\t          path: /etc/coreos/update.conf\n22\t    systemd:\n23\t      units:\n24\t        -\n25\t          dropins:\n26\t            -\n27\t              contents: |\n28\t                  [Service]\n29\t                  Environment=\"DOCKER_OPTS=--log-opt max-size=50m --log-opt max-file=3\n30\t              name: 10-dockeropts.conf\n31\t          enabled: true\n32\t          name: docker.service\n33\t        -\n34\t          contents: |\n35\t              [Unit]\n36\t              Description=etcd (System Application Container) TLS assets\n37\t              ConditionFileNotEmpty=|!/etc/ssl/etcd/system:etcd-server:my-test-cluster-etcd-{{.etcd_index}}.installer.team.coreos.systems.crt\n38\t              ConditionFileNotEmpty=|!/etc/ssl/etcd/system:etcd-server:my-test-cluster-etcd-{{.etcd_index}}.installer.team.coreos.systems.key\n39\t              ConditionFileNotEmpty=|!/etc/ssl/etcd/system:etcd-peer:my-test-cluster-etcd-{{.etcd_index}}.installer.team.coreos.systems.crt\n40\t              ConditionFileNotEmpty=|!/etc/ssl/etcd/system:etcd-peer:my-test-cluster-etcd-{{.etcd_index}}.installer.team.coreos.systems.key\n41\t              Requires=docker.service\n42\t              After=docker.service\n4