{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_vrtx_01KX43VJxpkDAdk2b9uCWMzD","type":"tool_result","content":"/home/jsuri/random-testing/prashanth-help/machine-config-operator/docs/MachineConfigDaemon.md:72:Updates are provided via the `OSImageURL` component of a MachineConfig object.\n/home/jsuri/random-testing/prashanth-help/machine-config-operator/docs/MachineConfigDaemon.md:74:[cluster-version-operator](https://github.com/openshift/cluster-version-operator/),\n/home/jsuri/random-testing/prashanth-help/machine-config-operator/docs/MachineConfigDaemon.md:79:The `OSImageURL` refers to a container image that carries inside it an OSTree payload.  When\n/home/jsuri/random-testing/prashanth-help/machine-config-operator/docs/MachineConfigDaemon.md:80:the `OSImageURL` changes, it will be passed to the [pivot](https://github.com/openshift/pivot)","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_vrtx_01AmMi3GeEKAgb2HPrnNGvun","session_id":"97616e95-6991-412d-aaaf-43b45e95d486","uuid":"6fca2178-621d-4952-8b7e-2f08d26ccf97","timestamp":"2026-06-22T21:33:48.986Z","subagent_type":"Explore","task_description":"Find MachineConfig examples with remote file sources"}
